To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private LongLineCandle _longlinecandle;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_longlinecandle = LongLineCandle(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_longlinecandle.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "longlinecandle", _longlinecandle.Current.Value);
}
